Design, Develop and Implement a Program in C++ for converting an Infix Expression to Postfix Expression. The program should support for both parenthesized and free parenthesized expressions with the operators: +, -, *, /, %(Remainder), ^(Power) and alphanumeric operands.

Example:

Sample Inputs	
321*/+154

Sample Outputs
Output=321*/154+

#include<iostream>
  using namespace std;
  int main()
  {
      int i,y=0,ctr=0;
      char str[20],str2[20];
      cin>>str;
      
      for(i=0;str[i]!=NULL;i++){
          if(str[i]=='+')
          {ctr++;}
          else{
              str2[y++]=str[i];
          }
      }
      while(ctr!=0){
        str2[y++]='+';
        ctr--;  
      }
      
      str2[y]=NULL;
      
      cout<<"Output="<<str2;

      return 0;
  }
